Generally speaking, we try not to collect data from website visitors.
We don't set cookies, we don't use analytical tools, and we don't have ads.

For transparency sake, you can scroll down to see what we use (and what data we may collect) to administer our website, email, or whatever the case may be.

Rest assured: any data we do collect will be stored securely and handled in accordance with this privacy policy.

Last updated: December 24, 2021
(this policy is subject to change at any time)

**Google Workspace**
Used to administer:
General ops (emails), surveys, shared files

Collected data:
Names, email addresses

Data trashing policy:
Emails deleted after 1 year of receiving.
Survey data removed 60 days after ending.

Service privacy policy:
See this page. (https://policies.google.com/privacy)

